        "data": "<p>Reference the table below to learn more about compatible configurations for integrated technologies with Liferay Portal EE.</p>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 697px; float: left;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><strong>Technology</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><strong>Liferay Portal 6.2 EE</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\"><font size=\"2\"><strong>Liferay Portal 6.1 EE</strong></font></span></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Document Conversion</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">LibreOffice 3.6</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Microsoft Word 2003, 2007, 2010</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenOffice 2.3.x-3.2.x</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">LibreOffice 3.6</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Microsoft Word 2003, 2007</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenOffice 2.3.x-3.2.x</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">External Repository Connectors</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Alfresco 4.0</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Documentum 6.6</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Nuxeo 5.4.2</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Sharepoint 2010</span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Alfresco 3.4</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Documentum 6.6</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Nuxeo 5.4.2</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Sharepoint 2010</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">File Stores</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">AdvancedFileSystemStore</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">CMISStore</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">DBStore</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">FileSystemStore</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">S3Store</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">AdvancedFileSystemStore</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">CMISStore</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">DBStore</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">FileSystemStore</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">JCRStore</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">S3Store</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">File Stores (non-production)</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">JCRStore</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">LDAP Directories</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Apache Directory Server</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Microsoft Active Directory Server</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Novell eDirecrtory</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenLDAP</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<p><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Apache Directory Server</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Microsoft Active Directory Server</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Novell eDirecrtory</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenLDAP</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Node Discovery</span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">TCPPing</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">JDBC_Ping</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">S3_Ping</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">UDPPing</span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">TCPPing</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">JDBC_Ping</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">S3_Ping</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">UDPPing</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Preview Generation</span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Ghostscript 9.05+</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">ImageMagick 6.9.1-4</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PDFBox 1.8.12</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Xuggler 5.4</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">HTML5</span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Ghostscript 9.05+</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">ImageMagick 6.8.6.3-3</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PDFBox 1.6.0</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Xuggler 5.4</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SAML Implementations</span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">ADFS</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DE</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay Portal EE</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Oracle Access Manager</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenAM</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PingFederate</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Shibboleth</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Siteminder</span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">ADFS</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay DE</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Liferay Portal EE</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Oracle Access Manager</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenAM</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">PingFederate</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Shibboleth</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Siteminder</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Search/Indexing</span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Solr 3.5</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Solr 4.3.1-4.10.2</span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Integrated Lucene</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Solr 1.4.1</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Search/Indexing (non-production)</span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Integrated Lucene</span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\"> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SSO Implementations</span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SAML</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Facebook</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">NTLM</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Central Authentication Service (CAS)</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenID</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Atlassian Crowd</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenSSO</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Siteminder</span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">SAML</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Facebook</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">NTLM</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Central Authentication Service (CAS)</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenID</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Atlassian Crowd</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OpenSSO</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Siteminder</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 84px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\"><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">WebDav Client OS</span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">CentOS</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OSX Lion (10.7)</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows 7 and 8</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Ubuntu 10</span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 170px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 84px;\">\n<span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Linux</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">OSX</span><br><span class=\"wysiwyg-font-size-medium\">Windows XP, Vista, and 7</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>"
